## Ubuntu SOC Server Investigating RHEL Victim (No SIEM)

---

# üìå Project Purpose
This lab simulates a full cyber attack lifecycle against a RHEL endpoint monitored by an Ubuntu-based SOC workstation.  
The project demonstrates manual threat detection using native Linux logs and investigative tools without SIEM platforms.

---

# üß± Lab Architecture

| Role | Operating System | Purpose |
|------|-----------------|---------|
| SOC Server | Ubuntu | Monitoring & Investigation |
| Victim Host | RHEL | Simulated Enterprise Endpoint |


---

